Aegis
Discworld ritual help
Aegis

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Aegis - Protects a target against harm.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Aegis places your target under the protection of your god, reducing
any damage they incur.  The amount reduction will be based on
your ability to perform defensive rituals.  You need a prayer book and
a holy symbol consecrated to your god to perform this ritual.
.EP
